Launch Rover Mast

After launching rover using cool, easy method, open 2x new terminals

ssh into both terminals with 
ssh marvin_v2@192.168.1.80

In run terminal, run:
stty -F /dev/ttyUSB0 115200 raw -echo -echoe -echok

This sets up the port

To raise:
printf "raise\n" > /dev/ttyUSB0

To lower:
printf "lower\n" > /dev/ttyUSB0

To stow:
printf "stow\n" > /dev/ttyUSB0

In the second terminal, run the second script for optional debugging outputs:
cat /dev/ttyUSB0

You will get an output like this: 
